; Coverage for filters.cc lines 1641-1652 (rewrite_posts account rewrite)
; When account-rewrite directive matches, the posting is rewritten
; with a new account path.

account-rewrite  Expenses:Food  Expenses:Groceries

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Test                  Expenses:Groceries           $10.00       $10.00
24-Jan-01 Test                  Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
end test
